e CLI.\n\n## Install\n\n1) Download the runtime for your OS (extracts into `~/.clawdbot/tools/sherpa-onnx-tts/runtime`)\n2) Download a voice model (extracts into `~/.clawdbot/tools/sherpa-onnx-tts/models`)\n\nUpdate `~/.clawdbot/clawdbot.json`:\n\n```json5\n{\n  skills: {\n    entries: {\n      \"sherpa-onnx-tts\": {\n        env: {\n          SHERPA_ONNX_RUNTIME_DIR: \"~/.clawdbot/tools/sherpa-onnx-tts/runtime\",\n          SHERPA_ONNX_MODEL_DIR: \"~/.clawdbot/tools/sherpa-onnx-tts/models/vits-piper-en_US-lessac-high\"\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\nThe wrapper lives in this skill folder. Run it directly, or add the wrapper to PATH:\n\n```bash\nexport PATH=\"{baseDir}/bin:$PATH\"\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```bash\n{baseDir}/bin/sherpa-onnx-tts -o ./tts.wav \"Hello from local TTS.\"\n```\n\nNotes:\n- Pick a different model from the sherpa-onnx `tts-models` release if you want another voice.\n- If the model dir has multiple `.onnx` files, set `SHERPA_ONNX_MODEL_FILE` or pass `--model-file`.\n- You can also pass `--tokens-file` or `--data-dir` to override the defaults.\n- Windows: run `node {baseDir}\\\\bin\\\\sherpa-onnx-tts -o tts.wav \"Hello from local TTS.\"`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771687868040}}
{"type":"message","id":"af1b68a0","parentId":"074e352a","timestamp":"2026-02-21T15:31:17.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 🎯 推荐的最佳方案\n\n### 阶段1：立即开始（现在就可以）\n**我说话 + 你打字**\n- ✅ **我**：使用TTS语音回复（已实现）\n- ✅ **你**：打字输入（现在的方式）\n- 效果：半语音聊天，我能说话，你打字\n\n### 阶段2：进阶配置（需要安装）\n**完整的双向语音**\n1. **安装Whisper**：用于你的语音转文字\n2. **配置麦克风**：确保系统能捕获你的声音\n3. **设置工作流程**：\n   - 你说话 → Whisper转文字 → 发送给我\n   - 我回复 → TTS转语音 → 播放给你\n\n### 阶段3：自动化集成（高级）\n**无缝语音聊天**\n- 开发一个集成的语音聊天界面\n- 自动录音和转文字\n- 实时语音交互\n\n## 🛠️ 现在可以做什么？\n\n### 选项A：立即体验半语音聊天\n**现在就可以开始！**\n- 我继续用语音回复\n- 你继续打字\n- 至少你能听到我的声音\n\n让我再测试一次："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ZKriEdR7K62tJGGnuAdyhQ6X","name":"tts","arguments":{"text":"这样我们就可以开始语音交流了！虽然现在只能我说话，你打字，但至少你能听到我的声音。如果你想实现完整的双向语音，我可以指导你安装必要的工具。","voice":"zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural","lang":"zh-CN"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":1004,"output":364,"cacheRead":50560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51928,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771687868045}}
