{"type":"message","id":"77daa0f3","parentId":"2e95d536","timestamp":"2026-02-21T15:35:07.404Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你说得对！现在的语音文件需要你手动播放，确实不够实时。让我解释一下现状和解决方案：\n\n## 🎤 当前语音系统的限制\n\n### 问题所在：\n1. **我生成语音文件** → 保存到本地\n2. **你需要找到文件** → 手动播放\n3. **不是实时流** → 无法自动播放\n\n### 技术原因：\n- 我运行在服务器环境\n- 无法直接控制你的电脑音频输出\n- 语音文件需要下载后播放\n\n## 🔧 实时语音解决方案\n\n### 方案1：使用网页实时语音（推荐）\n我可以创建一个**网页语音聊天界面**，实现：\n- ✅ 自动播放语音\n- ✅ 无需找文件\n- ✅ 接近实时体验\n\n### 方案2：安装语音插件\n需要安装额外的组件来实现：\n- 自动播放功能\n- 系统集成\n- 实时语音流\n\n### 方案3：使用现有聊天平台\n如果我们在**支持语音的平台上**（如某些聊天应用），可以直接语音回复。\n\n## 🚀 立即尝试：网页语音方案\n\n让我创建一个简单的网页语音播放器："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_51qtsRrMnGKTE43vQZptNdLY","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"voice_chat.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>实时语音聊天 - OpenClaw</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        \n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            padding: 40px;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            max-width: 500px;\n            width: 100%;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        \n        .header {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        \n        .logo {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        \n        h1 {\n            color: #333;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 28px;\n        }\n        \n        .subtitle {\n            color: #666;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        \n        .voice-player {\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;\n        }\n        \n        .audio-controls {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn {\n            background: #4CAF50;\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            width: 60px;\n            height: 60px;\n            font-size: 24px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn:hover {\n            background: #45a049;\n            transform: scale(1.1);\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn:active {\n            transform: scale(0.95);\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn.stop {\n            background: #f44336;\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn.stop:hover {\n            background: #d32f2f;\n        }\n        \n        .voice-text {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;\n            text-align: left;\n            max-height: 200px;\n            overflow-y: auto;\n        }\n        \n        .voice-text h3 {\n            color: #333;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 18px;\n        }\n        \n        .voice-text p {\n            color: #555;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            font-size: 16px;\n        }\n        \n        .status {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            padding: 10px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n        }\n        \n        .status.playing {\n            background: #d4edda;\n            color: #155724;\n            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;\n        }\n        \n        .status.stopped {\n            background: #f8d7da;\n            color: #721c24;\n            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;\n        }\n        \n        .status.ready {\n            background: #d1ecf1;\n            color: #0c5460;\n            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;\n        }\n        \n        .test-buttons {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 10px;\n            justify-content: center;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n        \n        .test-btn {\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            background: #6c757d;\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 25px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background 0.3s ease;\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n        \n        .test-btn:hover {\n            background: #5a6268;\n        }\n        \n        .test-btn.primary {\n            background: #007bff;\n        }\n        \n        .test-btn.primary:hover {\n            background: #0056b3;\n        }\n        \n        .instructions {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background: #e9ecef;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        \n        .instructions h3 {\n            color: #333;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        \n        .instructions ol {\n            padding-left: 20px;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n        \n        .instructions li {\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n        \n        footer {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            color: #666;\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n        \n        @media (max-width: 600px) {\n            .container {\n                padding: 20px;\n            }\n            \n            .audio-controls {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                gap: 10px;\n            }\n            \n            .control-btn {\n                width: 70px;\n                height: 70px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <div class=\"logo\">🎤</div>\n            <h1>OpenClaw 语音聊天</h1>\n            <p class=\"subtitle\">实时语音交流体验</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"voice-player\">\n            <h2>当前语音播放器</h2>\n            <div class=\"audio-controls\">\n                <button class=\"control-btn\" id=\"playBtn\" onclick=\"playAudio()\">\n                    ▶️\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"control-btn stop\" id=\"stopBtn\" onclick=\"stopAudio()\">\n                    ⏹️\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"control-btn\" id=\"testBtn\" onclick=\"playTestAudio()\">\n                    🔈\n                </button>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"status ready\" id=\"status\">\n                准备就绪：点击播放按钮开始\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"voice-text\" id=\"voiceText\">\n                <h3>语音内容：</h3>\n                <p id=\"textContent\">等待语音加载...</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"test-buttons\">\n            <button class=\"test-btn primary\" onclick=\"loadWelcomeAudio()\">\n                欢迎语音\n            </button>\n            <button class=\"test-btn\" onclick=\"loadTestAudio()\">\n                测试语音\n            </button>\n            <button class=\"test-btn\" onclick=\"loadStoryAudio()\">\n                小故事\n            </button>\n            <button class=\"test-btn\" onclick=\"loadJokeAudio()\">\n                讲笑话\n            </button>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"instructions\">\n            <h3>使用说明：</h3>\n            <ol>\n                <li>点击上面的按钮选择语音内容</li>\n                <li>点击播放按钮 ▶️ 开始听语音</li>\n                <li>点击停止按钮 ⏹️ 停止播放</li>\n                <li>确保电脑音量已打开</li>\n                <li>使用耳机或扬声器获得最佳效果</li>\n            </ol>\n        </div>\n        \n        <footer>\n            <p>OpenClaw 语音系统 | 实时语音聊天体验</p>\n            <p>如果无法播放，请检查浏览器是否允许自动播放</p>\n        </footer>\n    </div>\n\n    <audio id=\"audioPlayer\" preload=\"auto\">\n        <source id=\"audioSource\" src=\"\" type=\"audio/mpeg\">\n        您的浏览器不支持音频播放\n    </audio>\n\n    <script>\n        // 音频元素\n        const audioPlayer = document.getElementById('audioPlayer');\n        const audioSource = document.getElementById('audioSource');\n        const statusElement = document.getElementById('status');\n        const textContentElement = document.getElementById('textContent');\n        \n        // 预定义的语音内容\n        const audioContents = {\n            welcome: {\n                url: '', // 将由后端生成\n                text: '欢迎使用OpenClaw语音聊天！我是你的AI助手，很高兴能用语音和你交流。虽然现在还需要手动播放，但至少我们可以实现语音对话了！'\n            },\n            test: {\n                url: '',\n                text: '测试！测试！一二三，三二一！这是语音测试。如果你能听到这段话，说明语音播放正常。现在让我们开始真正的对话吧！'\n            },\n            story: {\n                url: '',\n                text: '让我讲个小故事：有一天，一个程序员走进一家酒吧，对酒保说：\"给我来一杯代码。\"酒保问：\"什么代码？\"程序员说：\"随便，只要没有bug就行。\"酒保想了想，给了他一杯白开水，说：\"这个绝对没有bug。\"'\n            },\n            joke: {\n                url: '',\n                text: '为什么程序员总是分不清万圣节和圣诞节？因为 Oct 31 等于 Dec 25！哈哈，这是一个程序员笑话。Oct是八进制的31，Dec是十进制的25，在计算机里它们数值相等！'\n            }\n        };\n        \n        // 当前播放的内容\n        let currentAudio = null;\n        \n        // 更新状态显示\n        function updateStatus(message, type = 'ready') {\n            statusElement.textContent = message;\n            statusElement.className = `status ${type}`;\n        }\n        \n        // 播放音频\n        function playAudio() {\n            if (!currentAudio || !currentAudio.url) {\n                updateStatus('请先选择语音内容', 'stopped');\n                return;\n            }\n            \n            try {\n                audioPlayer.play();\n                updateStatus('正在播放语音...', 'playing');\n                \n                // 播放结束事件\n                audioPlayer.onended = function() {\n                    updateStatus('播放完成', 'ready');\n                };\n                \n                // 播放错误事件\n                audioPlayer.onerror = function() {\n                    updateStatus('播放失败，请检查音频文件', 'stopped');\n                };\n                \n            } catch (error) {\n                updateStatus(`播放错误: ${error.message}`, 'stopped');\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 停止音频\n        function stopAudio() {\n            audioPlayer.pause();\n            audioPlayer.currentTime = 0;\n            updateStatus('已停止播放', 'stopped');\n        }\n        \n        // 加载并播放测试音频\n        function playTestAudio() {\n            // 使用浏览器内置语音合成作为备选方案\n            if ('speechSynthesis' in window) {\n                const utterance = new SpeechSynthesisUtterance();\n                utterance.text = \"这是浏览器内置语音合成测试！如果你能听到这段话，说明浏览器语音功能正常。\";\n                utterance.lang = 'zh-CN';\n                utterance.rate = 1.0;\n                utterance.pitch = 1.0;\n                utterance.volume = 1.0;\n                \n                // 播放\n                speechSynthesis.speak(utterance);\n                updateStatus('使用浏览器语音合成播放中...', 'playing');\n                \n                utterance.onend = function() {\n                    updateStatus('浏览器语音播放完成', 'ready');\n                };\n            } else {\n                updateStatus('您的浏览器不支持语音合成', 'stopped');\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 加载欢迎语音\n        function loadWelcomeAudio() {\n            loadAudioContent('welcome');\n        }\n        \n        // 加载测试语音\n        function loadTestAudio() {\n            loadAudioContent('test');\n        }\n        \n        // 加载故事语音\n        function loadStoryAudio() {\n            loadAudioContent('story');\n        }\n        \n        // 加载笑话语音\n        function loadJokeAudio() {\n            loadAudioContent('joke');\n        }\n        \n        // 加载音频内容\n        function loadAudioContent(type) {\n            const content = audioContents[type];\n            if (!content) {\n                updateStatus('无效的语音类型', 'stopped');\n                return;\n            }\n            \n            // 更新显示文本\n            textContentElement.textContent = content.text;\n            \n            // 如果是预生成的文件，设置URL\n            if (content.url) {\n                audioSource.src = content.url;\n                audioPlayer.load();\n                currentAudio = content;\n                updateStatus(`已加载${type}语音，点击播放`, 'ready');\n            } else {\n                // 如果没有预生成文件，使用浏览器语音合成\n                updateStatus(`准备播放：${type}`, 'ready');\n                \n                // 使用浏览器语音合成\n                if ('speechSynthesis' in window) {\n                    const utterance = new SpeechSynthesisUtterance();\n                    utterance.text = content.text;\n                    utterance.lang = 'zh-CN';\n                    utterance.rate = 1.0;\n                    utterance.pitch = 1.0;\n                    utterance.volume = 1.0;\n                    \n                    // 存储当前内容\n                    currentAudio = {\n                        url: 'browser-tts',\n                        text: content.text\n                    };\n                    \n                    // 直接播放\n                    speechSynthesis.speak(utterance);\n                    updateStatus('浏览器语音合成播放中...', 'playing');\n                    \n                    utterance.onend = function() {\n                        updateStatus('播放完成', 'ready');\n                    };\n                    \n                    utterance.onerror = function(event) {\n                        updateStatus('语音合成错误', 'stopped');\n                    };\n                } else {\n                    updateStatus('您的浏览器不支持语音合成', 'stopped');\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 页面加载完成\n        window.addEventListener('load', function() {\n            updateStatus('语音播放器已就绪', 'ready');\n            \n            // 检查浏览器支持\n            if (!('speechSynthesis' in window)) {\n                updateStatus('提示：您的浏览器不支持内置语音合成，部分功能可能受限', 'stopped');\n            }\n            \n            // 自动加载欢迎语音\n            setTimeout(() => {\n                loadWelcomeAudio();\n            }, 1000);\n        });\n        \n        // 处理音频播放错误\n        audioPlayer.addEventListener('error', function(e) {\n            console.error('音频播放错误:', e);\n            updateStatus('音频播放失败，尝试使用浏览器语音合成', 'stopped');\n        });\n        \n        // 获取语音列表（如果需要从服务器获取）\n        async function fetchAudioList() {\n            try {\n                // 这里可以添加从服务器获取语音文件的逻辑\n                console.log('可以扩展为从服务器动态获取语音');\n            } catch (error) {\n                console.error('获取语音列表失败:', error);\n            }\n        }\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":79,"output":3598,"cacheRead":54016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57693,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771688041532}}
