{"type":"message","id":"034135e7","parentId":"87a8233e","timestamp":"2026-02-21T15:35:31.701Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_DfzjGmpmhdz8xw2JycPvWLQV","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: 语音通话\ndescription: 通过Clawdbot语音通话插件发起语音通话。\nmetadata: {\"clawdbot\":{\"emoji\":\"📞\",\"skillKey\":\"voice-call\",\"requires\":{\"config\":[\"plugins.entries.voice-call.enabled\"]}}}\n---\n\n# Voice Call\n\nUse the voice-call plugin to start or inspect calls (Twilio, Telnyx, Plivo, or mock).\n\n## CLI\n\n```bash\nclawdbot voicecall call --to \"+15555550123\" --message \"Hello from Clawdbot\"\nclawdbot voicecall status --call-id <id>\n```\n\n## Tool\n\nUse `voice_call` for agent-initiated calls.\n\nActions:\n- `initiate_call` (message, to?, mode?)\n- `continue_call` (callId, message)\n- `speak_to_user` (callId, message)\n- `end_call` (callId)\n- `get_status` (callId)\n\nNotes:\n- Requires the voice-call plugin to be enabled.\n- Plugin config lives under `plugins.entries.voice-call.config`.\n- Twilio config: `provider: \"twilio\"` + `twilio.accountSid/authToken` + `fromNumber`.\n- Telnyx config: `provider: \"telnyx\"` + `telnyx.apiKey/connectionId` + `fromNumber`.\n- Plivo config: `provider: \"plivo\"` + `plivo.authId/authToken` + `fromNumber`.\n- Dev fallback: `provider: \"mock\"` (no network).\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771688131696}}
{"type":"message","id":"8c8d9dad","parentId":"034135e7","timestamp":"2026-02-21T15:35:38.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 🎤 语音插件安装方案\n\n基于现有技能，我有以下语音插件方案：\n\n### 方案1：SAG + ElevenLabs（高级语音）\n**特点**：高质量语音，情感表达，mac风格体验\n**需要**：\n1. 安装 `sag` 命令行工具\n2. ElevenLabs API密钥\n3. 配置环境变量\n\n### 方案2：Sherpa-onnx TTS（本地离线）\n**特点**：完全离线，无需网络，隐私性好\n**需要**：\n1. 下载运行时和模型\n2. 配置环境变量\n3. 本地运行\n\n### 方案3：Voice-call插件（电话通话）\n**特点**：真正的语音通话，双向交流\n**需要**：\n1. 启用voice-call插件\n2. 配置电话服务商（Twilio等）\n3. 电话号码和API密钥\n\n### 方案4：增强现有TTS（最简单）\n**特点**：改进现有系统，自动播放\n**需要**：\n1. 创建自动播放脚本\n2. 系统集成\n3. 可能的小程序开发\n\n## 🔧 推荐安装步骤\n\n### 第一步：安装SAG（推荐）\n让我尝试安装SAG："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_FsMuTFRp6AfGx2s7XMDKDRrK","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sag --version"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":384,"output":307,"cacheRead":59328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60019,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771688131701}}
