{"type":"message","id":"aeaba391","parentId":"c5285d28","timestamp":"2026-02-21T15:45:12.851Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"太好了！自动播放能工作，这真是个好消息！🎉\n\n现在你想要**实时语音聊天**，这确实是语音交互的终极目标。让我分析一下实现方案：\n\n## 🎤 实时语音聊天的挑战与方案\n\n### 🔧 技术挑战：\n1. **双向语音流**：你说话 → 我听到，我说话 → 你听到\n2. **低延迟**：接近实时，无明显延迟\n3. **自动处理**：无需手动操作\n4. **稳定性**：连接可靠，不掉线\n\n### 🚀 实现方案（从易到难）：\n\n#### 方案1：网页实时语音（最快实现）\n**使用 WebRTC + 语音识别**\n- 网页内双向语音通话\n- 浏览器内置API支持\n- 需要开发前端界面和后端中转\n\n#### 方案2：桌面应用（更稳定）\n**使用 Python + 语音库**\n- 本地应用，性能更好\n- 可以集成更多功能\n- 需要安装和配置\n\n#### 方案3：现有平台集成（最方便）\n**使用支持语音的聊天平台**\n- 如Discord、Telegram语音功能\n- 利用现有基础设施\n- 平台限制较多\n\n#### 方案4：自定义语音服务器（最完整）\n**完整的语音聊天系统**\n- 最大控制权\n- 最佳用户体验\n- 开发复杂度最高\n\n## 🛠️ 立即开始的方案\n\n### 阶段1：网页实时语音原型（现在可以开始）\n\n让我创建一个**网页实时语音聊天原型**："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_S7SGmPSYaHFINr9KanlRa4RO","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\WH\\Desktop\\OpenClaw_Voice\\realtime_voice_chat.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>实时语音聊天 - OpenClaw</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        \n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2980, #26d0ce);\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            padding: 40px;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            max-width: 800px;\n            width: 100%;\n            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n        }\n        \n        .header {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n        \n        .logo {\n            font-size: 60px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite;\n        }\n        \n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.1); }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); }\n        }\n        \n        h1 {\n            color: #1a2980;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 32px;\n        }\n        \n        .subtitle {\n            color: #666;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        \n        .status-panel {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        \n        .status-card {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            padding: 25px;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        \n        .status-card.active {\n            border-color: #4CAF50;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.2);\n        }\n        \n        .status-card.recording {\n            border-color: #f44336;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(244, 67, 54, 0.2);\n        }\n        \n        .status-title {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #333;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 10px;\n        }\n        \n        .status-indicator {\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 12px;\n            height: 12px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: #ccc;\n        }\n        \n        .status-indicator.active {\n            background: #4CAF50;\n            animation: blink 1s infinite;\n        }\n        \n        .status-indicator.recording {\n            background: #f44336;\n            animation: blink 0.5s infinite;\n        }\n        \n        @keyframes blink {\n            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }\n            50% { opacity: 0.5; }\n        }\n        \n        .status-text {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #666;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        \n        .controls {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n            gap: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn {\n            padding: 18px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 10px;\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn.primary {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #45a049);\n            color: white;\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn.primary:hover:not(:disabled) {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #45a049, #3d8b40);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn.secondary {\n            background: #f0f0f0;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn.secondary:hover:not(:disabled) {\n            background: #e0e0e0;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn.danger {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f44336, #d32f2f);\n            color: white;\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn.danger:hover:not(:disabled) {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d32f2f, #b71c1c);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(244, 67, 54, 0.3);\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn:disabled {\n            opacity: 0.5;\n            cursor: not-allowed;\n            transform: none !important;\n        }\n        \n        .control-btn:active:not(:disabled) {\n            transform: translateY(0);\n        }\n        \n        .chat-area {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            padding: 25px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;\n            max-height: 300px;\n            overflow-y: auto;\n        }\n        \n        .chat-title {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #333;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 10px;\n        }\n        \n        .message {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            max-width: 80%;\n            animation: slideIn 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        \n        @keyframes slideIn {\n            from {\n                opacity: 0;\n                transform: translateY(10px);\n            }\n            to {\n                opacity: 1;\n                transform: translateY(0);\n            }\n        }\n        \n        .message.user {\n            background: #e3f2fd;\n            margin-left: auto;\n            border-bottom-right-radius: 5px;\n        }\n        \n        .message.ai {\n            background: #f5f5f5;\n            margin-right: auto;\n            border-bottom-left-radius: 5px;\n        }\n        \n        .message-header {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #666;\n        }\n        \n        .message-content {\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n        \n        .message.ai .message-content {\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        \n        .message.user .message-content {\n  